<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19991211.0120 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-11 14:06 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6045 &Cx1f; tad-z
u s BC-BKN-NBAWEST12-COX     12-11 0702
